      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not just a \"distortion\" though. i see the notifications, i see the way they look at me. it's real. and even if some people don't hate me, it doesn't even matter because it feels like there's no future anymore. everything is just... ruined. how am i even supposed to face tomorrow when it's just gonna be more of this?",
