      "content": "helplines and counselors just tell you the same thing. \"it gets better\" or \"stay strong.\" but they don't get it. they aren't the ones being humiliated every single day. it just feels like i'm trapped in a room that's getting smaller and smaller. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to be able to rest for real.",
